</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/6c225817c2d6d5cf49d17531f93b2102b24205d9" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.671ex; width:6.322ex; height:2.509ex;" alt="{\displaystyle c_{2}=0}"></span>.</li></ul>
<p>To generate the next number, <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle x_{3}}">
